item.title: By: Wildcricket
item.dc:creator: Wildcricket
item.description:
I guess I hit just the right level of absurdity with my name. No one else has it. And you can even pronounce it!
I did once have someone run up to me in Ironforge and comment that we had the same appearance. However, she was wearing a helm so it took a minute to figure out what the hell she was taking about.
